# Name
#    html/cal/wr.jnj.css
#
# Purpose
#    CSS fragment for calendar templates
#
# Revision Dates
#     3-Jan-2011 (CT) Creation
#     4-Jan-2011 (CT) Bug fixes
#    ««revision-date»»···
